{"tid":1271832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府其實好撚醒","createTime":"2019-07-01T07:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T17:26:08.000Z","uid":232190,"like":294,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8ddfd9c906acf6a7d0384520f12785dddfe5355c","tid":1271832,"uid":232190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:45:35.000Z","msg":"佢哋成撚日轉移視線，送中、明日大愚、國歌法，玩到我哋忙到死。<br />\n<br />\n擺到明佢哋係玩政治，我哋係玩抗爭<br />\n<br />\n我哋而家做緊嘅嘢9成反送中，到時監察會9fingfing又完，然後再做9義士。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋玩咗咁多年我哋都要成長啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而家收啲力放去成立獨立調查委員會去調查幾次衝突先，等警察道氣滅咗，下一次佢再二讀送中我哋先再做大佢。<br />\n<br />\n我哋學下佢哋轉移視線，等佢哋都忙下！我哋咁多人，佢哋得個班子，肯定發癲都似！</span>"},{"pid":"301427dfdee23c353572d848bc5d692941837bb2","tid":1271832,"uid":232190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:47:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a66b690b56f2ad459115ab621d933d9d330c55d","tid":1271832,"uid":232190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:47:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f37940e63ab669b571afd943c11792c725c989c3","tid":1271832,"uid":266837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:47:39.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ea28451dba9e32775bde9b57f1753e955d5240a1","tid":1271832,"uid":232190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:50:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"290f01061cc52b0f0a0ecdc53a1ede1cf19ffc5c","tid":1271832,"uid":232190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:50:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7f6bf9ad86e7bbadb4160cb46f2e23f9dfd420d","tid":1271832,"uid":259302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:51:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dbc106a98497ba06d7dd8183e83f24cc3dcf6bb3","tid":1271832,"uid":113373,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"成立獨立調查委員會為訴求重中之重"},{"pid":"c4feb8ceac0162cb142fe67c9b621598451394f4","tid":1271832,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"